&lt;h2 id="memorable-points"&gt;Memorable Points&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Background: Sere missiles can wipe out a city completely. Nyma&amp;rsquo;s nation has been
the only recipient of a seres strike. They&amp;rsquo;ve since acquired their own seres
stockpile. They&amp;rsquo;re engaged in war with an state that lacks seres weapons.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Stories of Your Life and Others</title><link>https://www.curiosities.dev/fiction/chiang-stories-of-your-life-and-others/</link><pubDate>Mon, 25 Oct 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.curiosities.dev/fiction/chiang-stories-of-your-life-and-others/</guid><description>&lt;div class="citation" citation-icon-class='fas fa-fw fa-book' cited-by-count='' is-main=''&gt;
